However, he can be rather selfish, cunning, opportunistic and restless!   Although this is Monkey Year, the luck for this swinging animal will be up and down, so he has to be cautious. He may be someone who likes good things in life but this year he must cut his lavish spending or he may be a sad Monkey inundated with debts.   Monkeys tend to look more for sex than for love (although there are exceptions).
